    "In addition, Google has partnered with major products including Product Hunt, Food Network, LinkedIn, Uber, [13]IFTTT, and Spotify to integrate them into Google Assistant, further expanding its capabilities, To provide users with more comprehensive and convenient intelligent assistant services.",
    "Google Assistant in different areas of applicationFirst of all, the application of Google Assistant in the field of smart homes can be described as the most prominent.",
